cu.explanation_en: Setting SCTP_OUTSTREAMS to 0 (invalid value) will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1-C connection establishment between CU and DU.

du.explanation_en: Setting SCTP_OUTSTREAMS to 0 (invalid value) will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1-C connection establishment between DU and CU.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SCTP_OUTSTREAMS 設定為 0（無效值）會導致 SCTP 關聯失敗，防止 DU 與 CU 之間建立 F1-C 連接。
